Din Guide respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our app.

1. Information We Collect
--------------------------
Din Guide does NOT collect any personally identifiable information from users.

2. Usage Data
-------------
We may collect limited, non-personal usage data such as:
- Device type and model
- Operating system version
- Anonymous usage statistics (e.g., screen views, feature usage)

This information helps us improve the app's performance and user experience.

3. No Internet Dependency
-------------------------
Din Guide is primarily an offline Islamic app. Any online features (if any) are optional and do not require personal information.

4. No Third-Party Sharing
-------------------------
We do not sell, share, or transfer your information to third-party companies or services.

5. Ads & Analytics
------------------
Our app does not include ads or third-party analytics that track you.

6. Data Security
----------------
We take all reasonable steps to ensure your data (if any) is protected. Since we do not store any personal data, the risk of misuse is minimal.

